Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.63,0:04:06.85,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\frz16.98\move(966.4,897.6,880,525)}*咚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.85,kakushigoto cover,,0,0,0,,{\p1\frx4\fry2\fscx552\fscy661\frz17.99\move(160,1300,118.4,1091.2)}m 0 0 l 0 -36 l 0 -36 l 20 -36 l 20 0 l 0 0
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.85,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\frx5\fry7\move(199,1110,153,898,0,1156)\frz288.7}贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:09.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真懷念  是「雞雞復雞雞」麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以前經常模仿這個還被大人訓過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:18.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂  我說過不准帶我的單行本到工作室來的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這…這是私人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:21.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你以為我是為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:25.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把每週畫的原稿送去遠處的倉庫放著？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:29.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為了什麼把這兒裝修得不像漫畫家的工作室？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,萬一姬來這兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:35.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是被姬知道了父親在畫充滿著大量黃段子的羞人漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是被姬知道了該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,她會封閉內心  不管說什麼都回答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「有什麼想說的事情就用漫畫來講呀」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是被這樣說了爸爸我就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:51.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便這麼說  能瞞到何時呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你才來的可能還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:05:00.15,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fade(315,0)\pos(1241.2,915.2)}主助手  志治仰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:05:00.15,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an9}註：與日語「請求指示」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:57.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師為了不被發現  在家穿著正裝出門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在途中換裝後才來這個工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:06.28,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)\pos(198.4,867.2)}新人助手  芥子驅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:06.28,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：與日語「教唆」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那為什麼不直接穿著正裝畫？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不穿成那種鬆散的樣子會畫不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且那樣都算好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:12.66,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\c&H16161D&\frz9.276\frx12\fry2\pos(1369.334,958)}作者近照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以前可是不全裸就畫不出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,算是創作者的日常了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:21.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不過  後藤老師的情況該叫做雞常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:27.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  他也歷經了千辛萬苦才變成現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,自從小姬出生以來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:34.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬的爸爸  在做什麼工作呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:36.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  有在工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:40.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:43.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不可以問別人爸爸媽媽的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師這樣說過的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:49.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,個人情報會和職業歧視掛鈎的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吧  老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是呢  不能強行地去問呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:56.71,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fade(321,0)\pos(1224,904)}班主任  六條一子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,切  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:00.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是個好孩子呢  小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我認為漫畫家也是很棒的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要向小姬隱瞞呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,話先說在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可不是畫的海賊王和麵包超人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:12.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「雞雞復雞雞」我有讀過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:18.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也是後藤老師的粉絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:24.73,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\move(1628,140,1621,245,2500,0)}復雞雞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:24.73,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\move(342,418,330,510,2500,0)}復雞雞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請不要再提起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:26.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是在姬面前這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可不知道我會有什麼下場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  後藤老師還挺有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我認為再自信一點也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:41.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,世間對漫畫家的認知  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:43.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,根本就不懂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊後藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:50.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我從其他的客人那兒聽到的  說你是漫畫家？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看吧  果然很有名嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:56.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,於是呢  周圍的孩子都來拜託我要色紙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你能畫點光之美少女麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:06.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且畫得還很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:09.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,換責編？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是新責編十丸院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,讀者贈品的T恤做好了我這就送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又換責編了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,交接工作有好好做麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟老師有很多麻煩的禁止事項嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:29.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,迷路了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會不會是搞錯地點去您家裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙都幹了什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是編輯去家裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:48.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫畫家這件事不就向姬暴露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:52.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:08:01.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是會搞錯送去家裡的糊塗編輯什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:03.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:06.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還真有！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.34,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,350)\pos(204.8,977.067)}編輯  十丸院五月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.34,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：與日語「停止印刷機」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:09.96,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\frz6.44\pos(900,176)}風之緊身褲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:09.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作為贈品的T恤  我帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:11.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還穿上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是新責編十丸院五月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,初次見面  我是後藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:22.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感覺…位置有點奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我去倒爸爸那份茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,慢慢倒喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙來幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,來找茬的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明我是為了讓你高興才穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:42.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也不想穿啊  這種羞人的T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:44.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以我不早說了要做可以穿的類型麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在做讀者贈品的T恤時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作者有時會提出做「可以穿出去的類型」這種要求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:58.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為有著「把角色大大地印在T恤上穿不出去的吧」的顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就有了簡單的純文字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,隨便做的剪影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,仔細看小點是角色的頭像等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:09.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣的話是什麼漫畫的贈品不就搞不清楚了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:10.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就用普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:12.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,給我脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,職權騷擾！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那就遮住這個圖案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:16.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,儘量自然點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:21.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大人物？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我去拿點高級甜點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:29.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會被認為是比父親年輕的上司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,給我重做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是媽媽麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這…這是什麼解讀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:49.27,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fade(234,0)\pos(364,70.133)}抱胸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:49.27,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fade(234,0)\pos(242.4,506.134)}大人物（CEO）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:49.27,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fade(234,0)\pos(237.333,570.667)}防止母乳漏出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:49.27,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fade(234,0)\pos(344,1012)}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:47.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快用其他的方式遮住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,糕點師傅嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,鋼琴老師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,主持人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:59.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個  該說是腦迴路清奇還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,先入為主的觀念也太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:01.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我去換杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:06.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:09.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您打算怎麼弄？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看好了  新責編
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我這十幾年可不是白畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我的工作就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作畫工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,改得看不出原來的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:27.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,重新作畫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:32.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畫成光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您沒有自尊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:35.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:45.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天被問到父親的工作了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回答說有在工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姑且不算是無職…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:54.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,無職  是指那些沒有在工作的人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒上色的地方也是叫無色的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:01.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,兩邊都…無職和無色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:01.01,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：無色和無職發音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:03.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:07.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那麼  各種顏色都能滿滿地塗上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,無論什麼顏色都能塗上去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬說得挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:16.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天來的人是CEO？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,穿著T恤好像是個大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:21.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬還懂CEO這種詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:22.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:25.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我在全球財經衛星上看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.24,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：東京電視台上播出的夜間財經新聞節目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個時間段…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,早點睡吧  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,誰來幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,貓咪要沖走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個  能否告訴我您的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,區區名字  不足掛齒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能說得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.73,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&HD0CFD4&\3c&H404653&\frz8.172\move(186.933,159.2,132,116)}救助貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.73,kakushigoto in 8,,0,0,0,,{\frz8.622\move(705.733,146.4,721,114)}地區新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.73,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\frz7.789\pos(637.066,503.867)}漫畫家立大功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.73,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\move(277.333,712,225,730)\frz7.45\c&H3A4151&\3c&H434C62&}被救貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.73,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz277.1\c&H677283&\3c&HFFFFFF&\move(742.4,625.067,720,640)}救命甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是暴露了可怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爬上坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:01.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這條作為區域劃分界線的舊山大道被夾在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:02.90,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(450.667,375.333)}目黑區
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:02.90,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1313.333,376)}澀谷區
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:03.91,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(450.667,375.333)}目黑區
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:03.91,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1313.333,376)}澀谷區
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我由此改變職業
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:06.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對  我的隱瞞之事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是作畫工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼還不趕緊變乾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:14.67,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}濕漉漉  濕漉漉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:17.17,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz334.2\pos(1051.2,579.2)}願望之事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.67,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\frz270\c&H2A3E5E&\pos(848,251.2)\frx4\fry14}希望能游
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.67,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H2A3E5E&\pos(795.2,438.4)\frx6\fry16}25
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.67,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\frz270\c&H2A3E5E&\pos(849.6,489.6)\frx2\fry16}米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果要掛在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:24.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我該寫什麼願望  爸爸才會高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:26.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,媽媽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:29.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,男人的全部就是出人頭地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是變得了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:33.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,變得了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:35.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.81,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\frz270\c&H51475A&\pos(780.8,305.6)}希望爸爸變得了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,了不起…指的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您怎麼突然成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對漫畫家來說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:48.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,了不起就是作品暢銷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要怎麼做才能賣得好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,順帶一提  最近較為暢銷的是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:59.09,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\pos(1353.6,380.8)\frz254.7}進擊的亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:59.09,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2\frz255.4\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\pos(1904,774)}東京飯種
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:01.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要畫黑暗奇幻類型的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您在胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:08.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明平日裡說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「我才不會迎合世人」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼  我只是在迎合姬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,賣得好就是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是腐朽的資本主義蠢豬想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:23.48,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(225.6,972.8)}助手  筧亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:23.48,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：名字來源為漫畫技法「陰影描繪」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:20.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,筧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉  我這麼陰暗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:27.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那除了賣得好以外  還有什麼能算是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:28.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫豪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:32.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正是漫豪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:34.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,芒果？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.41,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：日語中漫豪與芒果同音，此處為黃段子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是文豪的漫畫家版本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不也有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然賣得不好但卻有著巨大影響力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實  我已經想到是誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒想到你會來拜託我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:55.14,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fs58\shad2\c&H102A53&\4c&H103B73&\pos(812.534,660.267)}黑暗奇幻類型的巨匠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:55.14,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\shad2\c&H102A53&\4c&H103B73&\pos(750.4,700.8)}漫畫家  不二多勝日郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:55.14,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：原型為漫畫家藤田和日郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:51.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想要我教你怎麼畫黑暗奇幻漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你以前倒是賣得挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:54.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒禮貌的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在就有些「穩定」囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:03.15,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fade(150,100)\pos(1196.8,851.2)}穩定=賣不出去的委婉說法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:04.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,黑暗奇幻就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畫的時候會有「哇」的這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後再「嗚哇」地收尾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就「哇」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:15.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,向這傢伙請教  我也真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫豪還真是可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫  豪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,自己說些讓人摸不著頭腦的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還覺得可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要再講像「漫豪」這樣奇怪的說法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然說我是漫豪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是變成我的代名詞了可怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:35.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:38.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬居然會想要我出人頭地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:45.57,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\frz327.3\pos(1046.8,103.6)}進擊的亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:45.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可畫不來盔甲和怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,各位  你們怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼大家的臉色看上去都慘不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那肯定會慘不忍睹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,黑暗奇幻？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:15:00.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不讓作者畫自己想畫的東西正是編輯的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:04.84,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(518.4,732.8)\c&H41424D&}不讓作者畫自己想畫的東西是編輯的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:04.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不讓作者畫自己想畫的東西是編輯的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:04.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是指
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:09.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果讓正火的作者畫太多自己想要畫的在下一部作品裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:09.01,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs50\frz270\pos(1728,593.6)}畫什麼都可以喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:09.09,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs50\frz270\pos(368,235.2)}那我就畫時空穿梭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:12.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有時會導致作者因自負而失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:14.60,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frx26\fry350\frz243\c&H5B4BC4&\pos(1184,353.6)}退返
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這句話則是勸誡這種事的箴言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那位十丸院先生看上去居然有些可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:21.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不讓漫畫家畫自己想畫的東西正是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又不是我想畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:24.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:31.61,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,0)\pos(225.6,876.8)}助手  墨田羅砂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:31.61,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：與日語「別漏墨水」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,來晚了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的是太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  同學聚會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:40.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小羅砂現在居然在當週刊漫畫家助手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好厲害  是很有名的漫畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感覺拍了我好多彩虹屁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.71,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,150)\pos(358.4,758.4)\c&H3B3A4A&}不了解的人會有覺得在周刊漫畫當漫畫家助手的人很厲害的傾向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感覺已經走向人生巔峰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:50.01,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fade(250,0)\frz270\c&H498BF8&\3c&H411CB5&\pos(89.6,590.4)}了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:54.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會因為這種程度的依據就覺得自己了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟按照世間的評價
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,出名就等於了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:04.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為了實現姬想讓我變得了不起的這一願望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:06.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我只需要變得有名就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您這不本末倒置嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是變得有名了不就會被小姬發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,賣得好也大概會被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然只能選擇成為漫豪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:20.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:23.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}漫豪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有一位救助貓咪的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.88,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&H5F6A79&\pos(644.8,462.4)}救生圈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.88,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&H5F6A79&\pos(1482.4,490.4)}黑色西服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:31.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,超喜歡貓咪的我正在尋找這位不留名字的人  想要向他道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那我們得創立一個偵探團了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,聽上去好有意思  尋找犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然並不是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:39.93,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(336,942.4)}古武Silvia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:40.93,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1305.6,940.8)}東御雛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:41.93,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(339.2,944)}橘地莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:42.93,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1320,942.4)}後藤姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:47.31,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\frz272\c&H445069&\frx358\fry8\move(680,670,726.4,592,1350,0)}目黑川偵探事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:47.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小孩子們總喜歡立馬創立偵探團
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,根據目擊情報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:52.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,目標好像是往坡上的方向離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那我們去坡道上方尋找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:01.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸說坡上有叫潮人的怪物出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:04.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,潮人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能有怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:09.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:11.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,潮人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.92,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\pos(884.8,244.8)\c&H3A3947&}潮人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.92,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\pos(841.6,720)\c&H383846&}潮流人士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:15.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至少可以說是老師我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:16.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:19.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,潮人會去沒有漫畫的書店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後喝著如同咒語一般的飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:25.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師我可是好幾次在他們那兒吃了苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  要放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:30.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天回來的可真早  克拉克肯特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在是休息時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,店裡還是和往常一樣沒客人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天可是挺興隆的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:50.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒想到老師會是將工作場所選在這樣的潮流街上的潮人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:51.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在挖苦我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:53.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當然是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:58.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,住在這裡的潮人們  只對和自己有關的事有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:02.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒有人會來干涉  所以才覺得舒適是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:05.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也能夠安心去沒有漫畫賣的書店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,潮人  好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒事的  我會保護大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:18.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那位英雄  為什麼會去坡上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:22.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為他是英雄  說不定是來擊退怪物的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:25.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我撿到了一本漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:30.92,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\frz3.499\pos(907.2,241.6)}工作人員用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你可真沒有緊張感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:30.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們可不知道潮人會在什麼時候冒出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,出現了  怪物  潮人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:39.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:43.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說我是怪物  潮人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,究竟是在稱讚我還是貶低我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,究竟是哪個  小鬼們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  我都說了不要來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:54.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:57.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,傳說中拯救了貓咪的圈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:00.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,英雄來擊退怪物了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:03.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就像是黑暗奇幻的故事一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是被姬看見我這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我會死一百萬次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等等我們  勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:12.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們的黑暗奇幻冒險開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:14.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,進到那裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:20.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這裡就是書店？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:23.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看上去有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:26.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為這裡沒有放一本漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:32.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個難道就是一子老師說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.48,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1667.2,185.6)\c&H6E7275&}在沒有漫畫的書店…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.48,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&H6E7275&\pos(307.2,251.2)}喝著像咒語一樣的飲料…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,潮人的老巢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:40.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您點的大杯不含糖加巧克力棒和牛奶香蕉和堅果巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,加冰兩大杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感覺像是在詠唱咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:46.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快看那個標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:53.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然  就是潮人的老巢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這裡難道是星巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快看  在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:19:59.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,勇者大人來救我們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.13,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord3\c&HC12C64&\3c&HF857DC&\frz15.74\pos(276.8,619.2)}鬍子邋遢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:04.14,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord3\c&HC12C64&\3c&HF857DC&\frz359.7\pos(1552,16)}頭髮分叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:10.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不對  拯救貓咪的勇者大人怎麼可能是這麼骯髒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:13.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還在喝魔汁  他是怪物的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所提到的沒有漫畫…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.48,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\fade(120,0)\frz285.1\pos(723.2,227.2)\c&H292439&}沒有漫畫的書店
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.48,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\fade(120,0)\c&H292439&\frz278.8\pos(115.2,414.4)}沒有漫畫的書店
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怪物的弱點就是漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:19.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,剛才被人丟棄的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,吃我這招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:31.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這裡果然是星巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:31.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:39.00,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\frz275\pos(1282,353.6)}風之緊身褲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:45.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,發生了好多我無法理解的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:49.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然賣不出去是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:50.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:55.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天和朋友們一起玩了黑暗奇幻遊戲喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們從潮人那裡逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可不要玩危險的遊戲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:03.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:04.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要關燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:05.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:19.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要寫「希望爸爸變得了不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:21.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:22.30,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\frz270\c&H51475A&\pos(780.8,305.6)}希望爸爸變得了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我猜那樣會讓爸爸高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:31.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當然開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:35.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:38.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸最為開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最為開心的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:47.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,希望姬能夠健康快樂地長大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:51.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,健康  長大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那我就多喝點益力多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.75,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：日本乳酸菌飲料品牌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:22:00.96,kakushigoto in 2 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\frz270\pos(484.8,188.8)}希望姬能每天都過得開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:59.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣的話爸爸的那份快樂也拜託你了
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:24.11,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}くちびるつんと尖らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:24.11,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}架子十足地撅起嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:30.95,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}何かたくらむ表情は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:30.95,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}正在盤算著什麼企圖的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:36.08,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}別れの気配を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:36.08,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}將離別的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:45.84,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}ポケットに匿していたから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:45.84,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}隱藏在口袋中
